  <exercise label="ex_js_2">
    <statement>
      <p>Repeat the previous exercise but make a list of numbers.  In this case you will not be able to simply update the innerHTML of the paragraph, you will need to use the <c>document.createElement()</c> and <c>document.appendChild()</c> functions to add a new list item.</p>
